description.oldValue:
This feature enables customer administrators to see the release status of the Microsoft Teams, Outlook on the Web and Microsoft admin center features announced on Message center. The release status will provide information on features that are scheduled, rolling out, or completed on their tenant so they can efficiently plan for the change.
GA date: December CY2022
